flowchart LR
    USER[External Entity: User]

    subgraph PROCESS[Vaultword Processes]
        P1((1.0 Authenticate User))
        P2((2.0 Manage Vault Access))
        P3((3.0 Manage Credentials))
        P4((4.0 Generate Password))
    end

    subgraph DATASTORES[Data Stores]
        D1[(D1 Users)]
        D2[(D2 Encrypted Credentials)]
        D3[(D3 Local Session Data)]
    end

    USER -->|Email and password| P1
    P1 -->|User records read/write| D1
    P1 -->|JWT token| USER

    USER -->|Master password input| P2
    P2 -->|Session state update| D3
    P2 -->|Vault unlocked or locked state| USER

    USER -->|Add, view, update, delete requests| P3
    P3 -->|Encrypted credential write/read| D2
    P3 -->|Credential list and status| USER

    USER -->|Password generation options| P4
    P4 -->|Generated password| USER
    P4 -->|Optional generated value| P3
